<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbff071a9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s16061"><num value="16061">§ 16061.</num><heading> Hybrid vehicles</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall accelerate efforts directed toward the improvement of batteries and other rechargeable energy storage systems, power electronics, hybrid systems integration, and other technologies for use in hybrid vehicles.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbff071aa-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/58/tVII/s711">Pub. L. 109–58, title VII, § 711</ref>, <date date="2005-08-08">Aug. 8, 2005</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/119/818">119 Stat. 818</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
